Help for SET SAYCALLER:

This option when turned on will prefix any &nick& SAY
or ACTION command messages with the caller's nickname.

Syntax: SET <channel> SAYCALLER {ON|OFF}

Examples:
    /msg &nick& SET #ChatZone SAYCALLER ON
    /msg &nick& SET #ChatZone SAYCALLER OFF